\[\frac{x - y}{x^4 + y^4 + 6} \le \frac{2\sqrt[4]{x^4 + y^4}}{3\sqrt[4]{x^4 + y^4 + 6}} = \frac{2\sqrt[4]{(x^4 + y^4 + 6 - 6)}}{3\sqrt[4]{x^4 + y^4 + 6}} = \frac{2}{3}.\]
